Description:
You come to a place where you see a small rat man fiddling with cooking utensils and strange ingredients.

As you approach he explains that he is planning to enter a cooking competition somewhere in the upper ruins, for which he has to bring a main ingredient and prepare a dish there.
DescriptionAction: He asks you if you can help him to choose the main ingredient among some of the ones he has already selected and to prepare the dish during the competition.
